nodes.text: CH-33Z was a MSE-6 series repair droid. At one point in the Day Star Hotel, the Chadra-Fan Vosa stood atop the MSE series droid while she spoke to her spy, Faddey. Sometime later, he appeared on a New Republic Correctional Transport and was shot by Burg.[source?]

CH-33Z first appeared on The Star Wars Show as a side-character interacting with hosts Anthony Carboni and Andi Gutierrez. He made cameos in both The Mandalorian and Jedi Temple Challenge. He also appeared on a limited edition statue in celebration of The Star Wars Show's 100th episode.
